nix commands


find big dir 

du -hsx * | sort -rh | head -10

longest line in the file

awk '{ if ( length > x ) { x = length; y = $0 } }END{ print y }' error.log


recursive directory search with delete of file type

sudo find . -type f  -name '*.m3u' -delete

revursive directoy search find everyting but the file 


sudo find . -type f ! -name '*.m3u' 
